Tominanga River ( Lake Mahalona ) – 3 ex. (
ZMB 29072
), approx. 1.5 km east of Lake Mahalona , 02°38.73'S , 121°31.95'E , loc. 59- 03, on leaf litter, coll. K. & T . von Rintelen ,
